fimafeng 0.3

provision script for aegir by milk
https://github.com/milkmiruku/fimafeng

this is a script for my setup. you are responsible for using it! checks the script first, somethings might break on your system. to add checks for portablity. 

note:
shflags - uses getopt - no long flags on some systems

usage:
./fimafeng.sh --help

required:
/var/aegir/ff/ - containing this script
/var/aegir/ff/base/ - containing base make/info files
/var/aegir/ff/projects - contains project profile (.make/.info/theme) git repos (initial clone from /base)


history:
0.3 - 25/12/2011 - further refactored the whole thing.
